TimeSheetLineAgileEntityInfo - Class in com.ppm.integration.agilesdk.tm
This class stores relation information to agile tools for a Timesheet Line.
It will be used to look if there's a PPM Work plan that's integrated with the same entities, and automatically relate this timesheet line to the Project if it has timesheeting enabled.
